             <table class="contentpaneopen">
              <tbody>
               <tr>
                <td width="100%" class="contentheading">
                 <a class="contentpagetitle" href="/2011/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=615:uhc-school-hockey-tournaments&catid=1:latest-news&Itemid=2">
                  UHC School Hockey Tournaments
                 </a>
                </td>
               </tr>
              </tbody>
             </table>
             <table class="contentpaneopen">
              <tbody>
               <tr>
                <td valign="top" class="createdate">
                 Friday, 27 November 2015 09:19
                </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                <td valign="top">
                 <p>
                  Uddingston Hockey Club  are proud to announce that we will be running two School Hockey Tournaments on the  1st and 3rd of December at our new purpose built water based Astro turf pitch at Uddingston Cricket &amp; Sports Club.
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  UHC will have up to 600 children playing hockey over the two days all from Primary 6. The festival has had to be held over two days due to the growth of UHC's in school programme where 15 primary schools regularly receive coaching over the course of the year.
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  The festival is celebrating the hard work pupils have put in during the  first two terms of the academic year practicing hockey during curricular class PE sessions.
                  <br />
                  <br />
                  Games played during two hour sessions in the morning (9:30-11:30am) and afternoon (12:00-2:00pm).
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  There are 12 schools involved from both North and South Lanarkshire:
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  Bothwell Primary School
                  <br />
                  Muiredge Primary School
                  <br />
                  St. John the Baptist Primary School
                  <br />
                  St. Brides Primary School
                  <br />
                  St. Mary's Primary School
                  <br />
                  Aitkinhead Primary School
                  <br />
                  Tannochside Primary School
                  <br />
                  Hamilton college Primary School
                  <br />
                  Fernhill Primary School
                  <br />
                  Thorntree Primary School
                  <br />
                  Wellshot Primary School
                  <br />
                  QuarryBrae Primary School
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  UHC would like to take the opportunity to thank all the schools and teachers  and Palazzo kitchen and bathrooms for all their help and support during 2015.
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  <a title="View Palazzo Kitchens" target="_blank" href="http://www.palazzokitchens.com">
                   <img alt="2015112701" src="/2011/images/stories/images/news/2015/2015112701.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" />
                  </a>
                  <img alt="2015101103" src="/2011/images/stories/images/news/2015/2015101103.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" />
                 </p>
